## Key audit matters

Key audit matters are those matters that, in our professional judgement, were of most sign/i.rightficance in our audit of the financ/i.rightal statements of the current period and include the most sign/i.rightficant assessed risks of material misstatement (whether or not due to fraud) that we ident/i.rightfied. These matters included those which had the greatest effect on: the overall audit strategy, the allocation of resources in the audit; and direct/i.rightng the efforts of the engagement team. These matters were addressed in the context of our audit of the financ/i.rightal statements as a whole, and in our opin/i.righton thereon, and we do not provide a separate opin/i.righton on these matters.

